  <brief_title>How Can Rehospitalisations of Patients With Schizophrenia be Avoided? A Comparison Between Different Compliance Programs</brief_title>
  <official_title>How Can Rehospitalisations of Patients With Schizophrenia be Avoided? A Comparison Between Different Compliance Programs</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Technische Universität München</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Technische Universität München</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Participation in one of the three interventions psychoeducation by professionals,
      psychoeducation by peer-moderators, or video-education can reduce the rehospitalisation rate
      of patients with schizophrenia compared to a control group.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
